OL,3,CWelsh tourist attraction at risk of
OL,4,Cclosure as council aims to save money
OL,6,FA popular tourist attraction in Wales
OL,7,Fis at risk of closure after a council
OL,8,Fsaid it is forced to make "difficult
OL,9,Ffinancial decisions" to balance its
OL,10,Fbooks.
OL,12,FLlancaiach Fawr Manor, in Caerphilly
OL,13,Fcounty, could see its doors close for
OL,14,Fgood from later this year.
