OL,3,CWelsh tourist attraction at risk of
OL,4,Cclosure as council aims to save money
OL,6,FThe historic manor, which has been
OL,7,Frestored and furnished to imitate life
OL,8,Fin the 17th century, is run by
OL,9,FCaerphilly County Borough Council,
OL,10,Fwhich has been looking for ways to
OL,11,Fsave money. You can watch ITV Wales'
OL,12,FITVX report from the manor here.
OL,14,FCouncil leader Sean Morgan said the
OL,15,Fcouncil "can't continue to run our
OL,16,Fservices in the way we always have".
OL,18,FThe council currently provides an
OL,19,Fannual subsidy of #485,000 to run the
OL,20,Fvenue, but that will end from the end
OL,21,Fof this year.
