OL,3,CWelsh tourist attraction at risk of
OL,4,Cclosure as council aims to save money
OL,6,FIf the proposal is approved, the manor
OL,7,Fwill close from December this year,
OL,8,Fwith other options of how the facility
OL,9,Fwould be run set to be explored.
OL,11,FThe council has said the 20 members of
OL,12,Fstaff working at the manor are being
OL,13,Fsupported.
OL,15,FAlong with the Llancaiach Fawr Manor,
OL,16,FCaerphilly Council is also proposing
OL,17,Fto withdraw its current #347,000 per
OL,18,Fyear subsidy to run Blackwood Miners'
OL,19,FInstitute.
