OL,3,CWelsh tourist attraction at risk of
OL,4,Cclosure as council aims to save money
OL,6,FThe performing arts theatre in
OL,7,FBlackwood would also close at the end
OL,8,Fof December if the proposal is
OL,9,Fapproved.
OL,11,FCllr Morgan said: "We need to explore
OL,12,Fall options and consider ways of doing
OL,13,Fthings differently.
OL,15,F"I want to be honest with the
OL,16,Fcommunity, because it is clear that
OL,17,Fthe scale of savings means we need to
OL,18,Fmake some very difficult decisions
OL,19,Fover the coming months."
